  <description><![CDATA[<p>On the waterfront, just a couple of minutes’ walk from the harbour and Harstad centre, this stylish hotel offers wonderful views of the Vågsfjorden from its rooftop restaurant and some rooms. The hotel is one of Harstad’s most modern with good facilities including bar, breakfast and dining room on the ground floor, top floor panoramic restaurant, small fitness room and free Wi-Fi throughout. All the bedrooms have bath or shower, TV, telephone, minibar and hairdryer. Free tea and coffee is available throughout the day.</p>]]></description>
